{
  "stem": "16163.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I don't really have [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a recollection of what happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything was sort of drama, you know, like you didn't know what would happen to you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told us we were going to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what we anticipated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no idea what would be what, really.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where they were talking about, all the people and sick people concentrating in Theresienstadt in the ghetto, which to us sounded better than going to Poland to the east.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But even then we didn't know what it meant to go to these, really, I mean, in details what to expect.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we knew, but don't think it-- anybody really expected what was coming and what had he hit a lot of people already.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I had family who went to [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Russia. ?] I had friends from Vlotho who went to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My uncle and my aunt from [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Krefeld ?] went to Lublin, and I remember us getting postcards from there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you still didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You still had no idea what it really was that was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The postcards-- I remember one card.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were certain things which I didn't want to eat as a kid and it was now the whole family knew I wouldn't eat this, right?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my aunt and uncle on the card wrote, [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Miriam ?] would be very happy if she could sauerkraut again-- if she could eat sauerkraut again over here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that meant as-- they had made out with my parents like a word to mention if things were bad.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this must have been one of the things that I would be happy, even if I could get that to eat.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's one of the items I never would eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
